一樣比人歧視<br />\n<br />\n大多數種族歧視人既人都係D讀書唔成，又窮又懶既廢人<br />\n最叻只係用自己種族優勢（例如黑人比較高大）又或者種族既歷史（例如白人創造世界好多既野）黎歧視其他人換取優越感<br />\n基本上依個唔係中國人，亦唔係東亞人既問題<br />\n<br />\n難聽d都要講句，中國人好多既低等行為外國人一樣做好多<br />\n隨地吐痰、隨地大小便、唔衛生依d...你去歐美一次就見得清清楚楚<br />\n所以外國人歧視東亞人，唔係完全只係因為中國人低等行為<br />\n而係冇野搵野黎恰"},{"pid":"b95e2f6d18205f178f5fde53d949ebc3131b0408","tid":2238424,"uid":141033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fbc25248ecbb41ee9b318f7ecc11d2fb0ca9d56","tid":2238424,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"跟本就係d爛仔恰鳩人<br />\n同racist無乜關係<br />\n佢覺得你唔會反抗就會恰鳩你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"點解唔係兩樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fffdd4d814def806183f361078ca45144ec058b","tid":2238424,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"337b110c92c74b0b536fd9c5cca0d80d19235f53","tid":2238424,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"個look係幾似支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}